---
import ComponentDoc from '../../layouts/ComponentDoc.astro';
import Section from '@esa/docs/Section.astro';
---
<ComponentDoc name="Data Grid" category="Data" slug="esa-grid" type="reference" wraps="AG Grid"
  summary="<code>esa-grid</code> is a thin Ecology skin over <strong>AG Grid</strong> (<code>ag-grid-angular</code> / <code>ag-grid-community</code>). It owns the column model, selection, sorting, pagination, quick-filter, and a set of Ecology cell renderers — then themes the underlying AG Grid DOM with design tokens.">

  <Section id="overview" title="Overview">
    <div class="ref-banner">
      Non-functional reference. This page documents the wrapper around AG Grid
      (or an equivalent such as TanStack Table) behind the API below. The mock
      further down is static HTML styled with Ecology tokens — it approximates the
      rendered grid but does not sort, select, or scroll.
    </div>
    <h3 class="sub">What it wraps</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Third-party library:</strong> AG Grid Community (<code>ag-grid-angular</code>, <code>ag-grid-community</code>).</li>
      <li><strong>Why a wrapper:</strong> AG Grid handles virtual scrolling, column virtualization, sort, filter, and pagination engine. Ecology contributes the column convention (<code>EsaGridColumn</code>), a config object with sane defaults, typed event payloads, themed DOM via <code>::ng-deep</code>, and five reusable cell renderers.</li>
      <li><strong>Swappable:</strong> the public API (<code>columnDefs</code>, <code>rowData</code>, <code>config</code>, output events) is engine-agnostic enough to re-target TanStack Table if licensing or bundle size demanded it.</li>
    </ul>
  </Section>

  <Section id="api" title="API">
    <h3 class="sub">Inputs</h3>
    <div class="api-table">
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Input</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Purpose</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><code>columnDefs</code></td><td><code>EsaGridColumn&lt;T&gt;[]</code></td><td><em>required</em></td><td>Column definitions (extends AG Grid <code>ColDef</code> with <code>esaRenderer</code>).</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>rowData</code></td><td><code>T[]</code></td><td><em>required</em></td><td>Row data array.</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>config</code></td><td><code>EsaGridConfig</code></td><td><code>{'{}'}</code></td><td>High-level options, merged with <code>ESA_GRID_DEFAULTS</code>.</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>agGridOptions</code></td><td><code>GridOptions</code></td><td><code>{'{}'}</code></td><td>Escape hatch for any raw AG Grid option.</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>quickFilterText</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><code>''</code></td><td>Free-text filter applied across all columns.</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h3 class="sub">Outputs</h3>
    <div class="api-table">
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Output</th><th>Payload</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><code>rowClicked</code></td><td><code>{`{ data: T; rowIndex: number }`}</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>selectionChanged</code></td><td><code>{`{ selectedRows: T[]; count: number }`}</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>sortChanged</code></td><td><code>{`{ columnId: string; direction: 'asc' | 'desc' | null }`}</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>pageChanged</code></td><td><code>{`{ page: number; pageSize: number }`}</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>gridReady</code></td><td><code>GridReadyEvent</code> (raw AG Grid api)</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="meta">Imperative methods: <code>getGridApi()</code>, <code>resizeColumns()</code>, <code>selectAll()</code>, <code>deselectAll()</code>.</p>
  </Section>

  <Section id="config" title="EsaGridConfig">
    <div class="api-table">
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Key</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><code>pagination</code></td><td><code>boolean</code></td><td><code>false</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>pageSize</code></td><td><code>number</code></td><td><code>100</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>pageSizeOptions</code></td><td><code>number[]</code></td><td><code>[25, 50, 100, 250]</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>rowSelection</code></td><td><code>'single' | 'multiple' | 'none'</code></td><td><code>'none'</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>showSelectionCheckbox</code></td><td><code>boolean</code></td><td><code>true</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>autoSizeStrategy</code></td><td><code>'fitContents' | 'fitGrid' | 'none'</code></td><td><code>'fitContents'</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>height</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><code>'calc(100vh - 20rem)'</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>suppressColumnMenu</code></td><td><code>boolean</code></td><td><code>false</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>quickFilterPlaceholder</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><code>'Search...'</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>enableTooltips</code></td><td><code>boolean</code></td><td><code>true</code></td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section id="anatomy" title="Anatomy & static mock">
    <p class="meta">Header row, selection checkbox column, hoverable / selectable body rows, and each of the five Ecology cell renderers in context.</p>

    <div class="mock-toolbar">
      <span class="mock-search">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
        Search…
      </span>
      <span class="mock-count">4 of 128 rows · 1 selected</span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-mock">
      <div class="grid-row grid-head">
        <div class="cell cell-check"><span class="chk"></span></div>
        <div class="cell">Site name <span class="sort">↓</span></div>
        <div class="cell">Status</div>
        <div class="cell">Permit #</div>
        <div class="cell cell-flag">Reviewed</div>
        <div class="cell cell-actions">Actions</div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-row is-selected">
        <div class="cell cell-check"><span class="chk chk-on"></span></div>
        <div class="cell"><a class="link-cell" href="#">Cedar Creek Outfall</a></div>
        <div class="cell"><span class="chip chip-success">Active</span></div>
        <div class="cell tip-cell">WA-0042189 <svg class="copy" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2"/><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"/></svg></div>
        <div class="cell cell-flag"><svg class="flag flag-on" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
        <div class="cell cell-actions"><button class="btn-cell btn-primary">Open</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-row">
        <div class="cell cell-check"><span class="chk"></span></div>
        <div class="cell"><a class="link-cell" href="#">North Fork Lagoon</a></div>
        <div class="cell"><span class="chip chip-warning">Pending</span></div>
        <div class="cell tip-cell">WA-0037744 <svg class="copy" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2"/><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"/></svg></div>
        <div class="cell cell-flag"><svg class="flag" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"/></svg></div>
        <div class="cell cell-actions"><button class="btn-cell btn-outline">Open</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-row">
        <div class="cell cell-check"><span class="chk"></span></div>
        <div class="cell"><a class="link-cell" href="#">Marsh Restoration B</a></div>
        <div class="cell">
          <span class="chips-wrap">
            <span class="chip chip-primary">Wetland</span>
            <span class="chip">Tidal</span>
            <span class="chip-overflow">+2 more</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="cell tip-cell">WA-0051002</div>
        <div class="cell cell-flag"><svg class="flag flag-on" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
        <div class="cell cell-actions"><button class="btn-cell btn-ghost">Review</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-row">
        <div class="cell cell-check"><span class="chk"></span></div>
        <div class="cell"><a class="link-cell" href="#">Estuary Monitoring 7</a></div>
        <div class="cell"><span class="chip chip-danger">Lapsed</span></div>
        <div class="cell tip-cell">WA-0029810</div>
        <div class="cell cell-flag"><svg class="flag" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"/></svg></div>
        <div class="cell cell-actions"><button class="btn-cell btn-primary" disabled>Open</button></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section id="renderers" title="Cell renderers">
    <p class="meta">
      Referenced by string via <code>esaRenderer</code> on a column, or by the
      AG Grid <code>cellRenderer</code> property. Each takes options through
      <code>cellRendererParams</code>.
    </p>
    <div class="api-table">
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Renderer (<code>esaRenderer</code>)</th><th>Key params</th><th>Renders</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><code>esaButton</code></td>
            <td><code>label, icon, variant ('primary'|'secondary'|'outline'|'ghost'), tooltip, disabled, onClick</code></td>
            <td>Inline action button.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><code>esaLink</code></td>
            <td><code>routerLinkBase, linkValue, linkDisplay, openInNewTab, externalHref</code></td>
            <td>Router or external link, truncated with ellipsis.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><code>esaChips</code></td>
            <td><code>getChips, maxVisible</code> · chip color: <code>default|primary|success|warning|danger</code></td>
            <td>Pill chips with optional icon + "+N more" overflow.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><code>esaTooltip</code></td>
            <td><code>tooltipText, copyOnClick, maxWidth</code></td>
            <td>Truncated text + native tooltip, optional copy-to-clipboard.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><code>esaCheckbox</code></td>
            <td><code>editable, onToggle</code></td>
            <td>Read-only check icon, or an interactive checkbox when editable.</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section id="tokens" title="Tokens">
    <p class="meta">The wrapper exposes <code>--grid-*</code> override hooks, each falling back to a semantic token. Consume these to re-skin AG Grid:</p>
    <ul class="tokens">
      <li><strong>Container:</strong> <code>--grid-border-color → --color-border</code>, <code>--grid-border-radius → --radius-300</code>, <code>--grid-shadow → --shadow-200</code>, <code>--grid-bg → --color-surface</code>.</li>
      <li><strong>Type:</strong> <code>--grid-font-family → --font-sans</code>, <code>--grid-font-size → --type-size-200</code>.</li>
      <li><strong>Header:</strong> <code>--grid-header-bg → --color-surface-sunken</code>, <code>--grid-header-text → --color-text-secondary</code>, <code>--grid-header-font-size → --type-size-100</code>.</li>
      <li><strong>Rows:</strong> <code>--grid-row-hover-bg → --color-hover-overlay</code>, <code>--grid-row-selected-bg → --color-active-overlay</code>, <code>--grid-row-border-color → --color-border</code>.</li>
      <li><strong>Cells:</strong> <code>--grid-cell-padding-x → --spacing-300</code>, <code>--grid-cell-padding-y → --spacing-200</code>; focus uses <code>--focus-ring-width</code> / <code>--focus-ring-color</code>.</li>
    </ul>
  </Section>
</ComponentDoc>

<style>
  .sub { font-size: var(--type-size-300, 1.125rem); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold, 550); margin: var(--spacing-500, 1.5rem) 0 var(--spacing-200, 0.5rem); }
  .lede { max-width: 70ch; }
  .ref-banner {
    padding: var(--spacing-300, 0.75rem) var(--spacing-400, 1rem);
    background: var(--color-warning-subtle, #fffbeb);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-warning-border, #fde68a);
    border-radius: var(--radius-200, 8px);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #525252);
    font-size: var(--type-size-150, 0.875rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-400, 1rem);
  }
  .meta { color: var(--color-text-muted, #737373); font-size: var(--type-size-150, 0.875rem); max-width: 72ch; }

  .api-table { overflow-x: auto; border: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e5e5e5); border-radius: var(--radius-200, 8px); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-300, 0.75rem); }
  .api-table table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; font-size: var(--type-size-150, 0.875rem); }
  .api-table th, .api-table td { text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-200, 0.5rem) var(--spacing-300, 0.75rem); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light, #efefef); vertical-align: top; }
  .api-table th { background: var(--color-surface-sunken, #efefef); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold, 550); }
  .api-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: 0; }

  .mock-toolbar { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--spacing-300, 0.75rem); flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-200, 0.5rem); }
  .mock-search { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-200, 0.5rem); padding: var(--spacing-200, 0.5rem) var(--spacing-300, 0.75rem); border: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e5e5e5); border-radius: var(--radius-200, 8px); color: var(--color-text-muted, #737373); font-size: var(--type-size-150, 0.875rem); min-width: 220px; }
  .mock-count { color: var(--color-text-muted, #737373); font-size: var(--type-size-100, 0.75rem); }

  .grid-mock {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e5e5e5);
    border-radius: var(--radius-300, 0.5rem);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-200, 0 4px 20px -4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06));
    overflow: hidden;
    font-size: var(--type-size-200, 0.9375rem);
  }
  .grid-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 44px minmax(160px,1.6fr) 1.4fr 1.1fr 90px 110px; align-items: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e5e5e5); }
  .grid-row:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .grid-head { background: var(--color-surface-sunken, #efefef); }
  .grid-head .cell { color: var(--color-text-secondary, #525252); font-size: var(--type-size-100, 0.75rem); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold, 550); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .grid-row.is-selected { background: var(--color-active-overlay, rgba(0,88,98,0.08)); }
  .cell { padding: var(--spacing-200, 0.5rem) var(--spacing-300, 0.75rem); min-width: 0; }
  .cell-check { display: flex; justify-content: center; }
  .cell-flag, .cell-actions { display: flex; }
  .cell-flag { justify-content: center; }

  .chk { width: 18px; height: 18px; border: 2px solid var(--color-border-strong, #d4d4d4); border-radius: var(--radius-100, 4px); display: inline-block; }
  .chk-on { background: var(--color-primary, #43608a); border-color: var(--color-primary, #43608a); position: relative; }
  .chk-on::after { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 4px; top: 1px; width: 5px; height: 9px; border: solid var(--color-text-inverse, #fff); border-width: 0 2px 2px 0; transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .sort { color: var(--color-text-muted, #737373); }

  .link-cell { color: var(--color-primary, #43608a); font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium, 450); text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; display: block; }

  .chips-wrap { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; align-items: center; }
  .chip { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: var(--radius-full, 9999px); font-size: var(--type-size-100, 0.75rem); font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium, 450); background: var(--color-surface-sunken, #efefef); color: var(--color-text-primary, #171717); white-space: nowrap; }
  .chip-primary { background: var(--color-info-subtle, #eff6ff); color: var(--color-primary, #43608a); }
  .chip-success { background: var(--color-success-subtle, #f0fdf4); color: var(--color-success, #22c55e); }
  .chip-warning { background: var(--color-warning-subtle, #fffbeb); color: var(--color-warning, #f59e0b); }
  .chip-danger { background: var(--color-danger-subtle, #fef2f2); color: var(--color-danger, #ef4444); }
  .chip-overflow { font-size: var(--type-size-100, 0.75rem); color: var(--color-text-muted, #737373); }

  .tip-cell { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; color: var(--color-text-primary, #171717); white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
  .tip-cell .copy { color: var(--color-text-muted, #737373); flex-shrink: 0; }

  .flag { color: var(--color-disabled-text, #a3a3a3); }
  .flag-on { color: var(--color-primary, #43608a); }

  .btn-cell { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 4px 12px; border: 1px solid transparent; border-radius: var(--radius-100, 4px); font-size: var(--type-size-100, 0.75rem); font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium, 450); font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--color-primary, #43608a); color: var(--color-text-inverse, #fff); }
  .btn-outline { background: transparent; border-color: var(--color-border, #e5e5e5); color: var(--color-text-primary, #171717); }
  .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--color-text-primary, #171717); }
  .btn-cell[disabled] { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }
</style>
